function Start(idActor, snoQuest)	
	idFollower = Hydra.QuestGetFollower("QST_NPC_Kehj_KIA_IronWolf_Follower")
	idQuestOwner = Hydra.QuestGetOwner()

	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idFollower) then
		Hydra.QuestFollowerTakeOwnership(idFollower)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(conv_IWFightEnd, idQuestOwner, idFollower)
		Hydra.QActorWait(idFollower, 2.0)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(conv_KIA_04a, idQuestOwner, idFollower)
		
		Hydra.QActorWaitForConversationFinished(idFollower, conv_KIA_04a)
		Hydra.QActorPlayConversation(conv_KIA_04b, idQuestOwner, idFollower)

		Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idFollower, loc_DawoodWalkTo, "NPC_WALK_FAST", true)
		Hydra.QActorDeletePersonalClone(idFollower, 1.5)
	end
		
end
